sentences: Franco Ambrosetti (born 10 December 1941) is a jazz trumpeter, flugelhornist and composer.
He was born in Lugano, Switzerland; his father, Flavio, was a saxophonist who once played opposite Charlie Parker.
Dado Moroni, Niels-Henning Orsted Pedersen, Bluesology (Dire, 1981)
Dino Betti van der Noot, Here Comes Springtime (Soul Note, 1985)
